race.description: North East Forklift Services Maiden Plate
race.comment: ESTIVAL (6) returned from a spell with a solid effort over 1100m at this track. Steps up in trip and maps well. Fitter and the 2kg claimer can boot her into the finish. HER LEGACY (11) is yet to fill a placing in two runs, the latest when sixth over 1200m at Swan Hill. Improvement to come and today could be the day. CHASING QUIVERS (5) form either side of a break has been very ordinary but strips fitter and gets her chance to feature. TAP DANCE (9) drew wide over 1200m at Ballarat on debut last start and failed to feature. Fares better at the draws today and look for an improved run. UPINTHECITY (10) worth consideration for wider plays.
